Package: TPEase
Type: Package
Title: Generic Framework to perform Target Population of Environments analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Florian Larue
Maintainer: Florian Larue <florian.larue@outlook.com>
Description: TPEase is a generic framework to perform analysis of 
  Target Population of Environments (TPE) by using a crop model. 
  Through an object-oriented approach (R6), 
  this package eases the TPE analysis byallowing users to cross 
  environmental information (soil, weather, crop managment) and 
  varietal information (genotypic parameters) and thus simulate plant responses 
  to a diversity of situations.
  TPEase also incapsulates methods for parameter estimation (using DEoptim), 
  weather data generation (using raster and Marksim), 
  parallel grid simulation (using parallel) and 
  data vizualisation (using ggplot2).
